---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Pan-Fried Halloumi with Fattoush Salad
description: Savour the flavours of the Middle East with this shawarma-inspired dish featuring halloumi seasoned with our Shawarma Spice Blend. This meal is rounded out with vibrant fattoush salad and crispy flatbread.

Ingredients: Flatbread (enriched wheat flour, water, canola oil, yogurt (milk ingredients, modified corn starch, carrageenan, pectin, active bacterial culture), milk, yeast, buttermilk, sugar, vinegar, salt, wheat gluten, corn flour, guar gum, vegetable monoglycerides, baking powder, soy lecithin, natural flavours, potassium sorbate, calcium propionate, sodium bicarbonate, sorbic acid, enzymes) (milk, soy, wheat) • Romaine Lettuce • Halloumi (pasteurized cow milk, pasteurized goat's and sheep's milk, rennet, salt, microbial enzyme, calcium chloride, dried mint) (milk) • Tomatoes • Sweet bell pepper • Lemon • Cucumber • Tahini sauce (water, tahini (sesame), modified corn starch, sugar, vinegar, salt, concentrated lemon juice, vegetable oil, garlic, canola oil, spices, natural flavour, soy lecithin, xanthan gum, citric acid, lactic acid, potassium sorbate, sodium benzoate, calcium disodium EDTA) (soy, sesame) • Shawarma spice blend (spices and herbs, sugars (sugar, corn syrup solids), garlic powder, salt, corn starch, onion powder, silicon dioxide) • Parsley • Garlic • Green onion.
